<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807132>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–6. Fannia, male, head, frontal view: (1) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (2) F. colazorrensis Durango Ramírez- Mora; (3) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (4) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (5) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (6) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype. Scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807132/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807134>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–12. Fannia, male, head, lateral view: (7) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (8) F. canicularis (Linnaeus); (9) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (10) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (11) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (12) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype. Scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807134/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807146>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17–28. Fannia, male, anterior view. (17–21) Hind leg: (17) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (18) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (19) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (20) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (21) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype; (22–27) Hind femur: (22) F. chibcha Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho; (23) F. dodgei Seago; (24) F. obscurinervis (Stein); (25) F. pijao Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho; (26) F. quimbaya Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho; (27) F. trimaculata (Stein); (28) Hind tibia, F. colazorrensis Durango & Ramírez-Mora. Scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807146/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807152>
    dc:description "FIGURES 29–36. Fannia, male, posterior view. (29–33) Hind leg: (29) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (30) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (31) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (32) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (33) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype; (34–36) Hind femur: (34) F. embera Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho; (35) F. grandis Malloch; (36) F. porce Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho. Scale 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807152/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807159>
    dc:description "FIGURES 37–42. Fannia, male. (37) Abdomen, dorsal view, F. pusio (Wiedemann); (38–42) Sternite V, ventral view: (38) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (39) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (40) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (41) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (42) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807162>
    dc:description "FIGURES 43–48. Fannia, male, epandrium, cercal plate and surstyli, dorsal view: (43) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (44) F. chingaza Grisales, Wolff & de Carvalho; (45) F. colazorrensis Durango & Ramírez-Mora; (46) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (47) F. femoralis (Stein); (48) F. flavicincta (Stein). Scale 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2807162/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807178>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–66. Fannia: male, epandrium, cercal plate and surstyli, lateral view: (62) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (63) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (64) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (65) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (66) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
