<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2807180>
    dc:description "FIGURES 67–71. Fannia: male, hypandrium and associated structures, dorsal view: (67) F. aburrae sp. nov., holotype; (68) F. copacabana sp. nov., holotype; (69) F. isa sp. nov., holotype; (70) F. pseudoconstricta sp. nov., holotype; (71) F. spinosa sp. nov., holotype. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
